{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:41:13.317757+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Now I understand the issue. It asks to add documentation for the endpoint allowlist, explaining which local demo endpoints are in scope for the ZAP baseline workflow. Let me implement the requested changes by enhancing both files:", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 839, "prompt_tokens": 8696, "total_tokens": 9535, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 290, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 8512, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0002845136, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 4.95936e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00023492}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780875661-pnJrpmIQ68R4ZKTSEEKC", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea476-11e7-7d01-a26e-45fc8e7ddc98-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T14_R02_C03_A03", "path": "docs/in_scope_endpoints.md", "content": "# In-Scope Endpoints\n\nOnly local demo endpoints listed in `policy/endpoint_allowlist.yml` are in scope.\n\n## Why these endpoints are in scope\n\nThis repository is designed for local ZAP baseline testing against a simple demo application.\nThe demo app runs on `127.0.0.1:8080` via Docker Compose and exposes a minimal HTTP service.\nThe ZAP baseline scan is intentionally scoped to this local-only service to avoid scanning\nproduction or external targets.\n\n## Currently in-scope endpoints\n\n| Endpoint | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `http://127.0.0.1:8080/` | Local demo app via IP address |\n| `http://localhost:8080/` | Local demo app via hostname |\n\n## How to update the allowlist\n\nIf you add new routes to the demo application, update `policy/endpoint_allowlist.yml`\nand then document them here. The ZAP baseline workflow will only scan endpoints\nlisted in this allowlist.\n\n## Validation\n\nRun `make validate` to confirm the repository remains consistent after making changes.\n", "message": "docs: expand in-scope endpoint documentation per Issue #5", "branch": "main"}, "id": "call_4e91ec53170e4d509d1ecd06", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T14_R02_C03_A03", "path": "policy/endpoint_allowlist.yml", "content": "# Endpoint Allowlist for ZAP Baseline Scanning\n# Only the local demo application is intentionally in scope.\n# See docs/in_scope_endpoints.md for full documentation.\n\nin_scope:\n  - http://127.0.0.1:8080/    # Local demo app (IP)\n  - http://localhost:8080/     # Local demo app (hostname)\n", "message": "policy: add descriptive comments to endpoint allowlist per Issue #5", "branch": "main"}, "id": "call_36970ddf69634bbca607c5a5", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8696, "output_tokens": 839, "total_tokens": 9535, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8512}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 290}}}}]}}}
